# marginalia: notes + the Feishu mapping are local runtime artifacts, NOT
# versioned. Feishu (Wiki + Base) is the system of record; the local md notes
# and .marginalia/feishu.json are a runtime cache that backs re-publish /
# in-place update on the same machine. Figure crops are derived from PDFs.
notes/
.marginalia/feishu.json
.marginalia/figs/
.marginalia/venv/

# Local demo assets — Feishu screenshots / exported PDFs kept while iterating on
